## Injection
### These rules watch for code injection by the ptrace facility.
### This could indicate someone trying to do something bad or just debugging
-a always,exit -F arch=b64 -S ptrace -F a0=0x4
-a always,exit -F arch=b64 -S ptrace -F a0=0x5
-a always,exit -F arch=b64 -S ptrace -F a0=0x6
